∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime] (h : p > 2),
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → a ≠ b →
    let F (n : ℕ) := Finset.sum (Finset.range (p - 1)) (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k)
    in F a % p ≠ F b % p

∀ {p : ℕ} (hp : p.Prime) (hodd : p ≠ 2) {a b : ℕ}, a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p →
  a ≠ b → (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * a ^ i) ≢ (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * b ^ i) [ZMOD p]

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Nat.Prime p] (a b : ℕ), a ≠ b → a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → 
  let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n^i in
  F(a) % p ≠ F(b) % p

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p % 2 = 1 →
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
  let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i in
  F a % p ≠ F b % p
∀ {p : ℕ} (hp : p.Prime) {a b : ℕ}, a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → a ≠ b → let F := λ n, Finset.sum (Finset.range (p - 1)) (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k) in F a % p ≠ F b % p
∀ (p : ℕ) [hp : Fact p.Prime] (a b : ℕ), a ≠ b → a ∈ finset.range p → b ∈ finset.range p → let F := λ n, finset.sum (finset.range (p - 1)) (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k) in F a ≢ F b [ZMOD p]

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p > 2 →
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
  let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i
  in ¬(F a ≡ F b [MOD p])
∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime] (n : ℕ) (a b : ℕ), p ≠ 2 → a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → let F := λ n, ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i in F a % p ≠ F b % p

∀ {p n a b : ℕ}, Nat.Prime p → p ≠ 2 → a ≠ b → a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → ((Finset.range (p - 1)).sum (λ k, (k + 1) * a ^ k)) ≢ (Finset.range (p - 1)).sum (λ k, (k + 1) * b ^ k) [MOD p]
∀ {p : ℕ} [Fact (Nat.Prime p)], p % 2 = 1 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → ¬(∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * a ^ i) ≡ (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * b ^ i) [ZMOD p]
